also has some bold font, but mostly in the headings; I think the additions
will be readily identified.)

I will be at the meeting but wanted to send this out ahead of time for
review by those who have the chance to review before the meeting.

We may have some subsantive issues in a couple of areas that I would rather
discuss in person; I am working to determine whether they really exist.

Dan Carroll



