Subject: Draft letter to Governor Davis


Based on a reading of various official reports and our discussion last week,
the attached draft letter attempts to capture a consensus on immediate term
strategies for dealing with the overall electrical energy situation. We
relied upon the ISO Action Plan for plans for generation and transmission.
We will look forward to your input at tomorrow's meeting as to whether these
items are on target or not. If for some reason you and/or your organization
can not attend our meeting please call, fax or email us your comments and
suggestions as soon as possible.

Thank you for your attention to this matter.

As a reminder we will be meeting tomorrow at 1:30 at the California
Chamber -- 1215 K Street, 14th Floor.




